QuestData.Title: Burying Suspicion
QuestData.Description:
It will do us no good to disguise yourself as Nelesis if word reaches Kel'Thuzad that she was slain.
You must ensure that no one who sees you enter the cave survives.
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill $1oa Lichsworn forces outside the House of Rituals.
QuestData.RewardText:
You left none behind to raise alarm? Good.
We can proceed with the plan.
